 TOOLBAR

 The HTML toolbar appears if you load a HTML file  or  if  you  switch  the
 editor  to HTML editing mode using the WWW gadget. The WWW gadget is added
 to the standard GoldED toolbar during installation  of  this  package.  It
 shows  a  symbolized  image. The HTML toolbar offers the following gadgets
 (from left to right, up to down):

 @{u}Description               Function                                        @{uu}

 Update browser            Sends page to WWW browser. This function may not
                           work  with  all  browsers. It requires that your
                           browser supports a "reload page" ARexx command.
                           See list of compatible @{"browsers" link browsers}.

 Style "bold"              Changes style of marked text to "bold"
 Style "underlined"        Changes style of marked text to "underlined"
 Style "italics"           Changes style of marked text to "italics"
 Style "centered"          Changes style of marked text to "centered"

 Style "Header 1"          Changes style of marked text to "Header 1"
