 Style "Header 3"          Changes style of marked text to "Header 3"
 Style "Header 4"          Changes style of marked text to "Header 4"
 Style "Header 5"          Changes style of marked text to "Header 5"
 Style "Header 6"          Changes style of marked text to "Header 6"

 Insert Image              Inserts new image
 Autosize                  Inserts width/height information

                           Inserts WIDTH/HEIGHT tags for  all  (local)  GIF
                           images  with  dimensions  directly read from the
                           files. Browsers can layout pages faster is these
                           tags  are  present:  layout can begin before all
                           images have been transferred.

 Insert List               Inserts new list
 Insert Table              Inserts new table
 Insert Form               Inserts new form (Form Wizard)

